John Webb Dillon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Webb_Dillon 0 John Webb Dillon (6 February 1877 – 20 December 1949) was an English actor. He appeared in 89 films between 1911 and 1947. He was born in London and died in Hollywood, California, USA. He was married to Catherine Urlau. John_Webb_Dillon ( 6_February_1877 – 20_December_1949 ) was an_English_actor .
